story.storyDescription: Lance: You’re not watching the meteor shower?
story.title: A Promise - Part 1

messages.text: You’re not watching the meteor shower?
Wait a second. Let me go look.
Wow I never saw so many at once before.
I wish you were here. Then we could enjoy it together.
After my meeting tomorrow I will be on the first plane home.
I think it was an earthquake.
The whole place just shook like crazy.
Yeah, some dishes didn’t make it but I’m fine.
Lance tell me what’s going on.
Is everything okay. What’s happening there.
I don’t know what I would do without you.
Fine just I’m on the balcony.
What part of be careful can’t you understand?
I will be careful. But if the fire gets too bad our house will be burnt too.
Here’s an idea. Call the fire department.
It looks crazy out there. Nobody even paying attention to the fire.
My heart can’t take much more of this.
I think a meteor just hit the earth...
As if I would. Some people are going down there though.
Tell me about it. So weird.
First the meteor shower, now a crash landing.
It’s like something out of a bad SciFi movie.
Well if they are coming for brains you’re safe.
Ha ha. Why do I date you again?
Some guys are poking at it and it moved.
The idiocy of our species baffles me at times.
I think they cracked it open.
Something is moving. There’s purple smoke coming from it.
Seriously Lance go back inside. Lock the doors and windows.
I thought you didn’t believe in aliens.
You really want to be near the people poking at something that fell from the sky.
Talk about opening scene to bad shit about to happen.
Just go inside. All of that weird shit doesn’t set right with me.
That’s normally how the world works, sweetheart.
You shouldn’t have gotten near that thing. Are you okay?
Maybe you should go to the ER.
It’s not that bad. I’m not sick I just...I feel wrong.
What do you mean you feel wrong?
I’m not sure. I just feel...off.
I can skip my meeting. I can be on the next plane home.
Don’t be silly. This is important to you. You need this meeting.
I need you more. If you’re sick I want to be there for you.
Don’t go quiet on me. It’s makes me worry more.
I’m okay. I just blacked out a little.
How you get blacked out and okay in the same sentence.
You worry too much. I’m fine.
At least call my mom. She’ll stay with you for the night.
The last thing I want is to spend a night with your mother.
Says the son of the dragon lady.
LOL. Okay she is that bad. But she’ll look after you when I can’t.
I’m not a kid. Plus I just walked back into the house.
I’m going to lay down. I will text you when I’m up again.
I told you I was fine.
3 A.M. I told you not to come home.
Lance I’m still in my hotel. I’m going to come home right after the meeting.
Shit 3 A.M. I have to be up again at 5.
I heard someone one the door. It woke me up.
Call the police. Lock the bedroom door.
Just stay in the room. Hide someone.
Shit. I knew I should have come home.
What hurts? Lance what’s going on.
I can’t. I don’t want to.
They want me to open the door.
Whatever you don’t don’t open the door.
Come on Lance you’re freaking me out.
I don’t want to open the door.
